    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600 mb-0">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Insurance premiums vary based on age, health history, location, coverage options, and deductible choices. Prices shown are estimates for healthy applicants. Comprehensive coverage requirements differ by individual situation. Always verify coverage details and current pricing directly with providers before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
